title: [HorribleSubs] Walkure Romanze - 09 [1080p].mkv
description:
Episode: 09
Episode length: 25 min
Anime type: TV Series
Air date: 02 December 2013
Description: [Mizuno Takahiro] is a student training to be a begleiter (knight`s assistant) at an academy where aspiring knights joust. He himself had come to this academy to train as a knight, after becoming the unrivaled junior champion in his own home country. However, an injury in a tournament`s finals forced him to withdraw. Instead, he decides to be a begleiter to one of the academy`s maiden knights and help her win. Source: ANN Note: The first episode was pre-aired at a special event on 29.09.2013, regular TV broadcast started on 07.10.2013.
